Add a Frontend with AWS Amplify
n the previous stages, we built a complete serverless API that evolved from hardcoded facts → database-driven → AI-enhanced. Now you'll create a beautiful web frontend so users can interact with your Cloud Fun Facts API through a browser.

This stage completes your full-stack serverless application using AWS Amplify for hosting.

Step 1: Create the Frontend Code
